text: Gertrude Gries (born 16 October 1924) was an Austrian gymnast. She competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1924 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Austrian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
